   M      Minimum charge rate
             Self explanatory.
   N      Normal rate
             Self explanatory.
   Q      Quantity rate
             Self explanatory.
   R      Class rate (Reduction on normal rate)
             Description to be provided.
   S      Class rate (Surcharge on normal rate)
             Description to be provided.

