  8395  Returnable package freight payment responsibility, coded

  Desc: To indicate responsibility for payment of return freight
        charges for packaging that is returnable.

  Repr: an..3

        1 Paid by customer
             Self explanatory.
        2 Free
             Self explanatory.
        3 Paid by supplier
             Self explanatory.
   ZZZ    Mutually defined
             Self explanatory.

